%h2 FAQ
%h4 Where do I start?
%p Click the Login/Sign Up button to login to an existing account or to make a new one.
%h4 What can I do with an account?
%p You can add a new product to sell, search and buy products available, or look at your user profile.
%h4 How do I search for a product?
%p On the homepage, enter the item that you're looking for. Once you click search, it'll return products that match your search.
.link_to_button
